ED_Title: Provisional programme of work and timetable of the First Committee for 2025
ED_DecisionText: At its 44th plenary meeting, on 2 December 2024, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee,   (Footnote: A/79/417, para. 8, Draft decision II.) approved the provisional programme of work and timetable of the Committee for 2024, as set out in the annex to the report of the Committee.   (Footnote: A/79/471.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
